[conversation_walking_guard_01]
{
	[text*]
	{
		choice = more;
		order = 0;
		screen_text = "I'd like to know what is causing these damn monsters to suddenly run amuck like a swarm of wasps. I've served in the Elddim town guard for 10 years and I've never seen the Krug this organized. They have always been a sneaky, back-stabbing race but generally they were too fearful of us to cause too much trouble. If it was only here I would put it down to some local Shaman of their's creating a jihad over some mumbo jumbo, but it's not. I've heard that the Krug uprising is all over the Kingdom and that's why most of the men have been withdrawn to protect Castle Ehb. Figures, most of the population's here in the Peninsula but the safety of the damn King & Country comes first.";
	}
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Regardless I'd keep out of the Great Northern Forest for now if I were you. The last patrols are long overdue and I've heard reports of krug's carcasses that have been torn to pieces like tissue paper! That's something that's best avoided for now.";
	}
}
